note right of StateGraph
  LangGraph is the runtime for all
  new agents. Supports:
    - Cycles + conditional branching
    - Human-in-the-loop
    - Time-travel / state inspection
    - Persistent multi-thread memory
  create_agent() wraps this runtime.
  create_react_agent() exposes the
  full graph API directly.
end note

note right of BaseCheckpointer
  Thread-level (per-conversation) memory.
  Stores full graph state snapshots.
  Distinct from BaseStore which is
  cross-thread long-term memory.
end note

